## mediationverse — Ecosystem Meta-Package

**Version**: 0.0.0.9000 (dev; not yet on CRAN)

Meta-package that loads the core mediation ecosystem: `medfit`, `probmed`,
`RMediation`, `medrobust`, `medsim`.

---

