|---------|------|-------|
| medfit | ✅ 0.2.0+ | Dropped from `Remotes`; pinned in `Imports (>= 0.2.0)` |
| RMediation | ✅ 1.5.0 | Released 2026-06-18 |
| probmed | ❌ | Still GitHub-only |
| medsim | ❌ | Still in `Remotes: Data-Wise/medsim` |
